{"tid":409053,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係垃圾","createTime":"2017-09-21T17:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T17:41:17.000Z","uid":132778,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7177f6363fb172d422dfd929623b7779916e183","tid":409053,"uid":132778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T17:31:02.000Z","msg":"咁多年 一直擺佢係心入面<br />\n以為對方都會咁<br />\n其實人地一早吾重視你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住佢拍拖之後分手 再拍拖又再分手<br />\n佢每拍一次拖 我心酸一次<br />\n佢每分一次手 我心痛一次<br />\n<br />\n之後再諗到 佢只會為別人而觸動<br />\n再吾會對自己有一絲留戀<br />\n而佢只會係失意既時候先會搵自己<br />\n而我又會二話不說咁出現係佢身邊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好明顯 我係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ec9169aadaf3fe475ac06f90e7661dd59e00d1","tid":409053,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T17:41:17.000Z","msg":"吾88"}]}